{"tid":1555210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日城浸之路無人講？","createTime":"2019-09-09T09:27:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T17:34:25.000Z","uid":200021,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b8a3c91d1c6271b96097f8a2ce85e709279c7c6a","tid":1555210,"uid":200021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:27:43.000Z","msg":"反修例風波持續，繼全港各區多間中學今早（9日)均有學生自發響應築人鏈活動後，至近中午時分，則由大學生接力，逾千名來自城大、浸大的學生及舊生，協力築成「城浸之路」。<br />\n<br />\n有學生認為，人鏈活動展現和理非團結力量，冀港府聆聽民意。本身是浸大的眾志成員周庭，亦有參與其中，她指行動本身未必可非常有效向政府施壓，但體現同路人互相扶持、共同堅持的信念，又寄語港人勿輕言放棄。<br />\n<br />\n「城浸之路」於上午11時集合，12時展開行動，並由浸大或城大作起點，雙方參與的學生途經歌和老街，延伸至對方校園，參與人士身穿黑衣及戴上口罩響應，又手牽手組成人鏈。<br />\n<br />\n浸大生：對話平台若只屬閉門式　只是哄騙技倆<br />\n<br />\n浸大文學院三年級生盧同學，今早先返回中學母校聲援，再趕到大學校園築人鏈。她認為，行動或可喚醒社會關注，「本身唔了解嘅市民，行過後或者會留意」。對於特首林鄭月娥提出撤回修例，她認為遠不足夠，「我哋要嘅係五大訴求」，盧同學又批評，港府所倡議的構建對話平台，如果屬於閉門形式，只是哄騙技倆，「想你袋住先，但我哋唔要選擇性對話同聆聽。」她指，倘學界發起全面罷課，會加入嚮應。<br />\n<br />\n浸大幼兒教育四年級劉同學，認為人鏈行動的視覺效果震撼，亦是爭取民意的良好手段，足可顯示港人的團結力量。她表示，對運動走向感到樂觀，因和理非與勇武有機結合，文宣工作亦成功散落社區，認為會有更多港人加入壯大。她認為，五大訴求不可缺，但爭取雙普選最重要，「可以自己揀特首，咁其他訴求自會達到」，雖然民選特首施政亦未必如人意，「但起碼條路係自己揀，無得怨。」<br />\n<br />\n烈日當空，浸大及城大的黑色人海連綿至兩間大學的校園外，他們高呼「光復香港、時代革命」、「沒有暴徒、只有暴政」等口號，又大唱《願榮光歸香港》等歌曲打氣。沿途是車路，不少司機專程開窗打氣，亦有人舉起拇指以示支持。<br />\n<br />\n同樣就讀浸大的周庭，亦有以學生身分出席，她指，自己今早本希望回中學母校聲援，不過受制於宵禁令，未能出門，幸趕及參與「城浸之路」。<br />\n<br />\n因有宵禁令　周庭慶幸趕及參與「城浸之路」<br />\n<br />\n她認為，政府拒納民意，經過三個月以來，抗爭者或已感疲累灰心，且走到今日，多人犠牲亦只得「撤回」兩個字，「甚至依家都未正式撤回」。周又稱，人鏈行動未必可非常有效向政府施壓，但同路人可互相扶持，共同堅持信念，且社會行動是否奏效，需要嘗試，「未試過係唔知道」。她相信今次是本港持久運動，倘愈來愈多人加入，「政府係咪仲咁頑固，無人知道，所以要堅持下去」。她又稱，本港警察濫權，已能為警察城市，倘現在選擇放棄，「香港會更絕望，我哋會咩都無。」<br />\n<br />\n浸大翻譯系宋同學則認為，不少中學生共同發聲，大學生擁抱知識，且更年長成熟，理應同行，她認為港府未有積極回應五大訴求，民怨難降溫。惟特首只委任兩名前高官賢達進入監警會，與民間要求成立獨立調查委員會的期望不符，「完全唔對嘴，難以服眾。」<br />\n<br />\n資料來源: 香港01<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EmVw2h9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEmVw2h9.png&h=b1861e09&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3aOywbv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3aOywbv.png&h=e7563551&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4wiOj4S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4wiOj4S.png&h=c3244747&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GcD28Yd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGcD28Yd.png&h=0d79b295&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rf2Lnie.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frf2Lnie.png&h=0e9140fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/emNO4wB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FemNO4wB.png&h=6b0227ab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jaLMRbC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjaLMRbC.png&h=e57f7e6f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8ZrL6KY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ZrL6KY.png&h=e419a418&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tYAQyp0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtYAQyp0.png&h=383b7a80&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U68uOYm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU68uOYm.png&h=4be98be5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BMXGE5k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBMXGE5k.png&h=26e5ab45&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U8WwhR1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU8WwhR1.png&h=9ef8ad10&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ediywb3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fediywb3.png&h=b3c1b4f8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w6KqniK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw6KqniK.png&h=3559d4fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s61Hpw5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs61Hpw5.png&h=5510ecf6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WvtuOYN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWvtuOYN.png&h=559a4127&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/upi28YO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fupi28YO.png&h=6c8e5c8e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QyRTwb9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQyRTwb9.png&h=4be3f5e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c7f5bfcc69588f09f2b385e75210eea7f0cf218","tid":1555210,"uid":200021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:30:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d609ed5f7300209c029364ca49519ce9608c0c","tid":1555210,"uid":23390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:32:40.000Z","msg":"[緊急] 救人！尋9.8晚銅鑼灣F出口目擊市民！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1555111\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1555111</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4862b2401a28dcba37963de859386a3142bf8fa1","tid":1555210,"uid":200021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:36:40.000Z","msg":"搞得咁辛苦 原來連登無人留意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"893018f4ce26c04b21444be51923398c00b3b31a","tid":1555210,"uid":136457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4862b2401a28dcba37963de859386a3142bf8fa1","tid":1555210,"uid":200021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:36:40.000Z","msg":"搞得咁辛苦 原來連登無人留意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:15:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />被wfc"},{"pid":"964be596ab89195cd3f26a8890935f9a1a1b2e22","tid":1555210,"uid":223208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c